data.meta_site_name: Carpe Librum: Be awesome. Read books.
data.text:
"Born to Read" was the first project competed when Elizabeth got her big Remington Noiseless typewriter--the one that started her collection--back from the repair shop. People often ask if it will offend the friend or family member they are getting it for. We always answer, "If this describes them, then they already know (and it usually makes them feel seen)."

Manila Tote with Black Print.

Double stitched to allow the tote to be filled full of books, groceries, or whatever the need may be.
